'''Bret "No Fret" Hanson''' was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] instructor who was in command of [[Alliance Training Center-5/Green Squad]]. He trained many groups, as well as helping defend the facility from at least one [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] attack. He once tracked the traitor [[Nik (Rebel)|Nik]] down and confronted him in a downtown alley in [[Rakati]]. When Nik threw a [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] at his feet, he immediately activated his [[Jetpack/Legends|jet pack]], propelling him from the brunt of the blast and allowing him to fire his [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] at Nik, causing Nik to fall unconscious and allowing Hanson to put binders on him after he had recovered from the blast, and take him to stand trial before the Rebel high command.

